Inshuti zanjye nshya

Nitwa Simo

Menyana n'inshuti zanjye nshya

Zizo, Lele, Sisa na Ayanda

Zizo akunda umupira w'amaguru

Lele akunda koga

Sisa akunda gukina kwihisha no gushakana

Ayanda akunda gusoma

Nishimiye ibintu byose inshuti zanjye zikunda

Nzakina umupira na Zizo

Rimwe na rimwe noge hamwe na Lele

Cyangwa nyine kwihisha ushaka hamwe na Sisa

Ngwino, ushake inshuti nshya kandi wishimishe

Mukine umupira hamwe

Mwogere hamwe

Mukine kwihisha hamwe

Cyangwa musome hamwe
